{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Use start or end of items to reposition\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 3 modes: TRACK, QUEUE & TIMELINE\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Set interval between items in seconds, frames or beats\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Optionally add time offset between groups of items with the same name\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Non-linear factor to create rallentando & accelerando\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Toggle to preserve overlapping items\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Toggle to preserve adjacent items\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Realtime mode\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Support moving envelope points with items\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Support NVK folder items\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Support ripple edit\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Can generate no GUI scripts using current values (useful to save presets or use in custom actions)\sa180\par}
